Just keep... Go on. Keep going.

294
00:27:38,471 --> 00:27:40,996
This is for television.
Don't look at the camera.

295
00:27:41,208 --> 00:27:43,699
Just go by like you're
fighting. Like you're fighting.

296
00:27:43,910 --> 00:27:45,707
Don't look at the camera.
It's for television.

297
00:27:45,912 --> 00:27:49,507
Just go through. Go through. Just
